# Dashboard List Component Pattern

Standalone, OnPush, signals-based. Follow `PersonListComponent` structure exactly.

## Signal State Structure

```typescript
// Search
searchInput = '';                                   // two-way bound to input
search = signal('');                                // debounced value
private searchTimeout: ReturnType<typeof setTimeout> | undefined;

// Filters
activeFilters = signal<Partial<FilterParams>>({});  // domain-specific filters

// Pagination
page = signal(1);
limit = signal(50);
totalItems = signal(0);
totalPages = computed(() => Math.ceil(this.totalItems() / this.limit()));

// Sort
sortBy = signal<string | undefined>(undefined);
sortOrder = signal<SortOrder | undefined>(undefined);

// Data
items = signal<Item[]>([]);
loading = signal(false);

// Columns
visibleColumnKeys = signal<string[]>(this.loadVisibleColumns());
visibleColumns = computed(() => ALL_COLUMNS.filter(c => this.visibleColumnKeys().includes(c.key)));
```

## Column Definitions

```typescript
const STORAGE_KEY = '<entity>-list-visible-columns';

export interface ColumnDef {
  key: string;
  label: string;            // Catalan
  defaultVisible: boolean;
  sortField?: string;       // maps to API sortBy; omit if not sortable
}

export const ALL_COLUMNS: ColumnDef[] = [
  { key: 'title', label: 'Títol', defaultVisible: true, sortField: 'title' },
  // ...
];
```

## Debounced Search (300ms)

```typescript
onSearchChange(value: string) {
  clearTimeout(this.searchTimeout);
  this.searchTimeout = setTimeout(() => {
    this.search.set(value);
    this.page.set(1);      // always reset page on filter change
    this.loadItems();
  }, 300);
}
```

## Sort Cycling: none → ASC → DESC → none

```typescript
onSortColumn(col: ColumnDef) {
  if (!col.sortField) return;
  const field = col.sortField;
  if (this.sortBy() !== field) {
    this.sortBy.set(field);
    this.sortOrder.set('ASC');
  } else if (this.sortOrder() === 'ASC') {
    this.sortOrder.set('DESC');
  } else {
    this.sortBy.set(undefined);
    this.sortOrder.set(undefined);
  }
  this.page.set(1);
  this.loadItems();
}
```

## Data Loading

```typescript
private loadItems() {
  this.loading.set(true);
  const sortBy = this.sortBy();
  const sortOrder = this.sortOrder();
  const filters: FilterParams = {
    search: this.search() || undefined,
    page: this.page(),
    limit: this.limit(),
    ...this.activeFilters(),
    ...(sortBy && sortOrder ? { sortBy, sortOrder } : {}),
  };
  this.service.getAll(filters).subscribe({
    next: (response) => {
      this.items.set(response.data);
      this.totalItems.set(response.meta.total);
      this.loading.set(false);
    },
    error: () => this.loading.set(false),
  });
}
```

## Key Rules

- **Reset page to 1** on every filter/sort/limit change
- **Pagination limits**: whitelist `[25, 50, 100]`
- **Column visibility**: persist to `localStorage` with `STORAGE_KEY`
- **Ellipsis pagination**: show 1…[current-2..current+2]…last when totalPages > 12
- **Row click**: `router.navigate(['/<entity>', id])`
- **Sync button**: `router.navigate(['/<entity>/sync'])`
- **UI text**: always Catalan (labels, buttons, messages)
